lead_paragraph: A men’s synchronized team has been barred from a meet at Stanford University, reinforcing an International Olympics Committee decision designating the sport as women only. The San Francisco Tsunami Swim Club’s team planned to perform an exhibition at the FINA World Masters Championships.
